msgstr ""
"Starshipit: De præcise forsendelsesomkostninger for levering %(picking_name)"
"s er nu %(final_carrier_price)s, men automatisk revurdering af salgsordrens "
"levering mislykkedes: %(e_so)s"

#. module: delivery_starshipit
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/delivery_starshipit/models/delivery_carrier.py:0
